{"tid":38382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解紅磡站轉綫既控制咁差？","createTime":"2016-12-14T01:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T03:05:08.000Z","uid":27435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb52a499154712719656ff2af92fa1a77035d428","tid":38382,"uid":27435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:32:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母東鐵轉西鐵綫架車永遠唔係對面月台<br />\n1，2號要上大堂再落返去3，4號<br />\n都算啦，個時間牌又唔準<br />\n顯示隔離月台下班仲有2分鐘，用半分鐘跑上跑落點知door closed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e5f25cf5d55d69b98aba77e5f1ef1f04e288e4","tid":38382,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想知，痴撚線㗎"},{"pid":"1a597bb56509fba7dc4ac3489d0f6f23a864a779","tid":38382,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:39:10.000Z","msg":"因為你呢頭屌完佢，果頭又要繼續搭佢啲車"},{"pid":"d139a2b60cf7fba18a3a58f3f63119fc53b49f19","tid":38382,"uid":19549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:41:50.000Z","msg":"終於有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1034003c315ff47a22c7ac2b61c5c9142dbc1dd0","tid":38382,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:44:16.000Z","msg":"終於有人講<br />\n對面線無車轉 一等要等5mins以上<br />\n過對面得一兩分鐘<br />\n仲要成班人迫死果一條電梯<br />\n點撚樣趕得切去<br />\nOn99"},{"pid":"f630ae8f939d5ae2b43fd4f9178970622c3e9d51","tid":38382,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:03:22.000Z","msg":"其實個重點係東鐵線<br />\n西鐵嗰面好準時，但東鐵就成日都唔準/ 遲開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4db101d81a18